    • Field Detail

      • GPU

        static final int GPU
        GPU mode on.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • HILLSKEW

        static final int HILLSKEW
        GPU hillskew support. Enables the Model.getUnskewedModel() API to get the unskewed model.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • NORMALS

        static final int NORMALS
        Requests normals be computed for models. Enables the Model.getVertexNormalsX() Model.getVertexNormalsY() Model.getVertexNormalsZ() API.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
